{"tid":197036,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國聯合航空超賣，暴力拖走機艙乘客 (2)","createTime":"2017-04-11T16:04:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-12T01:28:21.000Z","uid":82640,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c35d7940c0ccbbf5e3100b9c8694280cdfb920a0","tid":197036,"uid":82640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:04:57.000Z","msg":"內容大意：<br />\n。航班UA3411滿坐但有4名crew要上機去下一班<br />\n。職員叫價$800現金劵，須每次$50使用及有限期<br />\n。有乘客指$1600就會考慮，但UA經理笑咗聲無理<br />\n。無人自願轉下班機下，UA經理稱「電腦隨機」抽出4位乘客<br />\n。其中一名乘客表示自己是醫生，明早有重要病人會面，拒絕下機<br />\n。職員召喚警察強行拖走醫生乘客<br />\n。醫生乘客撞傷面部流血，需召喚醫護人員<br />\n。整個過程被錄影上傳網絡<br />\n<br />\n片： <a href=\"https://streamable.com/fy0y7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Ffy0y7&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=252ddd3a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/fy0y7</a><br />\n<br />\n片2 ： <a href=\"https://twitter.com/JayseDavid/status/851223662976004096\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJayseDavid%2Fstatus%2F851223662976004096&d=9UZ2u2zW0crxbo%2Bu43gMWQIBMskQiLF9ooRt%2FFIrCZo%3D&h=939ac350\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJayseDavid%2Fstatus%2F851223662976004096&h=fa103d34\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/JayseDavid/status/851223662976004096</a>"},{"pid":"b541f8511d6c3b6c14849b401002d8313ee1fb59","tid":197036,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:45:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9f0dc2cbadd1f5662981eff8117034a9413f24c","tid":197036,"uid":35505,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:46:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n集中返一邊講啦<br />\n<br />\n美國聯合航空超賣，暴力拖走機艙乘客 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/197000/page/1?ref=web\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/197000/page/1?ref=web</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"518bff78e1b6f1ab8550f018784f39953df4e754","tid":197036,"uid":59711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T16:57:45.000Z","msg":"垃圾國家係咁上下啦"},{"pid":"a3cb90a0ba61737ef1d6ae8bff9866a6c34ee49c","tid":197036,"uid":5787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T17:00:54.000Z","msg":"𧋦蟈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d9d1ce90b22648188e687146fcb560580aff8b2","tid":197036,"uid":87290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T22:02:25.000Z","msg":"又話re-accommodate, 咁快就跪低變forcibly-remove<br />\n<br />\nStatement from United Airlines CEO Oscar Munoz on United Express Flight 3411<br />\nApril 11, 2017<br />\n<br />\nThe truly horrific event that occurred on this flight has elicited many responses from all of us: outrage, anger, disappointment. I share all of those sentiments, and one above all: my deepest apologies for what happened. Like you, I continue to be disturbed by what happened on this flight and I deeply apologize to the customer forcibly removed and to all the customers aboard. No one should ever be mistreated this way.  <br />\n<br />\nI want you to know that we take full responsibility and we will work to make it right.  <br />\n<br />\nIt&rsquo;s never too late to do the right thing. I have committed to our customers and our employees that we are going to fix what&rsquo;s broken so this never happens again. This will include a thorough review of crew movement, our policies for incentivizing volunteers in these situations, how we handle oversold situations and an examination of how we partner with airport authorities and local law enforcement. We&rsquo;ll communicate the results of our review by April 30th. <br />\n<br />\nI promise you we will do better. <br />\n<br />\nSincerely,<br />\n<br />\nOscar"},{"pid":"21e1cdc47582b21e19f753d9e558691c370dfa89","tid":197